Wise Alert

Wise Alert is an SMS banking product that allows customers to receive to receive SMS notifications on their mobile phones or through their e-mail addresses or both, as and when the transactions occur on their accounts.

Features

  • Receive notifications when debit/credit transactions occur
  • Set a local currency limit above which an alert should be sent
  • Receive notifications when your salaries/ loans fall due

Benefits

  • Convenient – use service from anywhere
  • Easy to use – mobile phones/ emails are easily accessible
  • Affordable – within the budget of all
  • Flexible – ability to customize service
  • Ability to detect fraudulent transactions
